title: Chris Brown's ex Karrueche Tran files restraining order | Daily Mail Online
text: Chris Brown's ex-girlfriend Karrueche Tran files a restraining order against the singer claiming he 'threatened to kill' her Tran filed a restraining order asking that her ex Brown be kept away from her The model stated in legal documents the singer had threatened to kill her The beauty and the rapper dated for several years before splitting in 2015 In January the singer posted a video where he talked about stalking women Chris said: 'If I love you, b****, ain't nobody gonna have you. I'm gonna make you miserable'
